{
  "lines": [
    {
      "key": "17.0",
      "line_index": 17,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "ee25af64",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "──いただきますっ",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "23.0",
      "line_index": 23,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "c59b2417",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "（うん、旨い！　我ながら最高の揚げ加減のフライだな！）",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "26.0",
      "line_index": 26,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "16bbb663",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "揚げたての白身魚のフライを口に頬張り、うんうんと頷く。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "27.0",
      "line_index": 27,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "a88b0600",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "みんなも俺と同じ感想なのか、笑顔でフライを口に頬張り",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "27.2",
      "line_index": 27,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "a88b0600",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "夕飯が賑やかになっていく。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "30.0",
      "line_index": 30,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "21bf86ed",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "（日に日に料理の腕が上がってきているかも……。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "30.2",
      "line_index": 30,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "21bf86ed",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "俺ってエンジニアよりも料理人の方が向いているんじゃないか）",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "33.0",
      "line_index": 33,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "e5e4bf3",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "そんなことを思いながら、手を休めることなく",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "33.2",
      "line_index": 33,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "e5e4bf3",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "目の前の料理を頬張り続ける。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "36.0",
      "line_index": 36,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "c911b764",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "──ん？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "39.0",
      "line_index": 39,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "cb5634bb",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ふと机の下に何かの気配を感じ、何気なく視界を机の下に移す。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "40.0",
      "line_index": 40,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "9a057c3",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "すると──",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "44.0",
      "line_index": 44,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "335ba7b5",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "──ぅえっ！？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "51.0",
      "line_index": 51,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "c21c3a5a",
      "speaker": "メア",
      "ja": "（しー……♥）",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "53.0",
      "line_index": 53,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "2c3d1f9e",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "メアが何故か机の下にいて、思わず大声をあげそうになってしまう。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "54.0",
      "line_index": 54,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "a9022958",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "メアはにこやかに笑いながら、静かにするようにと人差し指を口に当てる。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "56.0",
      "line_index": 56,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "aaeddb4b",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "メアに言われるがままに俺は驚きの声を何とか飲み込む。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "57.0",
      "line_index": 57,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "8e8750ad",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "そしてもぞもぞと俺に近づき、股間に手を伸ばす。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "60.0",
      "line_index": 60,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "7b8f49b8",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "（ちょ……！　な、なにするつもりなんだ……！？）",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "66.0",
      "line_index": 66,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "9b55c20c",
      "speaker": "メア",
      "ja": "（ふふ……♥　大人しくしていてくださいね♥　",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "66.2",
      "line_index": 66,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "9b55c20c",
      "speaker": "メア",
      "ja": "今日の一日の疲れ、メアが癒してあげますから……♥）",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "80.0",
      "line_index": 80,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "5c7f3213",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "（ま、待って……こんなところで……ダメだって……！）",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "83.0",
      "line_index": 83,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "34acb07c",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "メアはゆっくりと口でチャックを降ろし始め、思わず腰を引く。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "84.0",
      "line_index": 84,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "b55d3ac3",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "しかしメアはがっちりと俺を掴み動けないようにして、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "84.2",
      "line_index": 84,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "b55d3ac3",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "さらにゆっくりとチャックを降ろしていく。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "87.0",
      "line_index": 87,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "59da4adc",
      "speaker": "メア",
      "ja": "（わぁ……♥　今日も一日頑張ったおちんちんさんの匂い……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "87.2",
      "line_index": 87,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "59da4adc",
      "speaker": "メア",
      "ja": "パンツ越しでも香ってきます♥）",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "89.0",
      "line_index": 89,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "842b90c4",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "むわっとした股間の匂いに笑顔になっていくメア。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "91.0",
      "line_index": 91,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "e8d6b6a0",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "恥ずかしさと周囲にバレないかの心配が入り混じり、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "91.2",
      "line_index": 91,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "e8d6b6a0",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "頭の中がパニックになっていく。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "94.0",
      "line_index": 94,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "1fd0742b",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "（メア、本当にやめてくれって。みんながいるんだぞ？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "94.2",
      "line_index": 94,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "1fd0742b",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "もしバレてしまったらどうするつもりなんだ？）",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "98.0",
      "line_index": 98,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "8be1b4a6",
      "speaker": "メア",
      "ja": "（うふふ♥　その時はその時ですよ♥）",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "100.0",
      "line_index": 100,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "8fa9d915",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "そしてメアはズボンのチャックをすべて降ろしてしまう。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "103.0",
      "line_index": 103,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "10113b28",
      "speaker": "メア",
      "ja": "（くんくん……♥　すごい匂い……オスって感じがして……はぁ～♥　",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "103.2",
      "line_index": 103,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "10113b28",
      "speaker": "メア",
      "ja": "匂いだけでおまんこがぐちゅぐちゅになってきてしまいます……♥）",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "106.0",
      "line_index": 106,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "fbd80d56",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "（やめろって……！　におい嗅ぐなって……！）",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "110.0",
      "line_index": 110,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "16a19cdd",
      "speaker": "メア",
      "ja": "（ふふっ♥　顔真っ赤ですね♥　可愛いです♥　",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "110.2",
      "line_index": 110,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "16a19cdd",
      "speaker": "メア",
      "ja": "もっともっと恥ずかしくしてあげますね♥）",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "113.0",
      "line_index": 113,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "3d9d8efa",
      "speaker": "メア",
      "ja": "（恥ずかしさは快感の最高のスパイスなんですから♥）",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "121.0",
      "line_index": 121,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "dbda38ef",
      "speaker": "メア",
      "ja": "（ふふふっ♥　おちんちんもうこんなに勃起させて……♥　れるぅ♥）",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "124.0",
      "line_index": 124,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "262977ad",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "（うう……！　メア、やめろって……声、出てしまう……くっ！）",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "127.0",
      "line_index": 127,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "8edc4cc0",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "パンツの中から引っ張り出され、ぶるんとメアの目の前に飛び出す肉棒。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "128.0",
      "line_index": 128,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "29754fd2",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "メアは匂いを嗅ぎながら舌を這わせ、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "128.2",
      "line_index": 128,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "29754fd2",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ざらざらした感触にゾクゾクしか快感が全身を走る。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "131.0",
      "line_index": 131,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "9b350268",
      "speaker": "メア",
      "ja": "（ちんちんの傘もこんなに開いて……れろっ♥）",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "134.0",
      "line_index": 134,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "5c17d52d",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "──はおっ！？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "140.0",
      "line_index": 140,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "f515f417",
      "speaker": "リリアン",
      "ja": "んんん？　突然声を出して……どうかなさいました？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "143.0",
      "line_index": 143,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "c258b9d8",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "うぇ！？　あ、ああ、その、スープが思いの外熱くて驚いて……ははは……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "146.0",
      "line_index": 146,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "45998df",
      "speaker": "リリアン",
      "ja": "そうですか、火傷しないように気をつけてくださいね",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "149.0",
      "line_index": 149,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "752ac3c4",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "（ば、バレて……いない……よかっ……うっ！？）",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "152.0",
      "line_index": 152,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "7ecaf642",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "気づかれなかったことに一安心した直後、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "152.2",
      "line_index": 152,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "7ecaf642",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "メアの舌を大きく動かし裏筋から竿を舐める。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "155.0",
      "line_index": 155,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "163f788c",
      "speaker": "メア",
      "ja": "（今おちんちんすごく跳ねて……カウパーがたくさん……♥　",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "155.2",
      "line_index": 155,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "163f788c",
      "speaker": "メア",
      "ja": "オスの匂いもさらに強くなって……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "155.4",
      "line_index": 155,
      "inline_index": 4,
      "line_hash": "163f788c",
      "speaker": "メア",
      "ja": "ああ、この濃厚な香り……たまらないです♥）",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "158.0",
      "line_index": 158,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "300f7d6b",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "（も、もう本当にやめろって……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "158.2",
      "line_index": 158,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "300f7d6b",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "これ以上されたら絶対にバレるから……！）",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "162.0",
      "line_index": 162,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "99b5ce6e",
      "speaker": "メア",
      "ja": "ちゅるっ♥　れるっ……♥　オスの味も濃厚になってきて……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "162.2",
      "line_index": 162,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "99b5ce6e",
      "speaker": "メア",
      "ja": "はぁぁ～♥　おまんこジンジンしてきます……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "162.4",
      "line_index": 162,
      "inline_index": 4,
      "line_hash": "99b5ce6e",
      "speaker": "メア",
      "ja": "子宮があなたのザーメン求めてしまっていますぅ♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "164.0",
      "line_index": 164,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "130c9708",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "メアは俺の制止する声を無視するように、どんどん激しく舌を動かす。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "165.0",
      "line_index": 165,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "ae71d79e",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "亀頭全体を舌でなぞられ、先走り溢れる鈴口を舌で穿られる。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "167.0",
      "line_index": 167,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "1aeada49",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "一切休むことなくフェラをし続け、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "167.2",
      "line_index": 167,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "1aeada49",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "射精感がどんどん強くなってきてしまう。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "170.0",
      "line_index": 170,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "2c8f7471",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "（メア……本当にやめてくれ……！　これ以上は……ううう……！！）",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "174.0",
      "line_index": 174,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "37f45816",
      "speaker": "メア",
      "ja": "（ああ♥　その切なそうな顔、すごく良いです♥　",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "174.2",
      "line_index": 174,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "37f45816",
      "speaker": "メア",
      "ja": "それに出したければご自由に出してください♥　",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "174.4",
      "line_index": 174,
      "inline_index": 4,
      "line_hash": "37f45816",
      "speaker": "メア",
      "ja": "メアがすべて飲み込みますから♥）",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "177.0",
      "line_index": 177,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "4e5e57bf",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "（そ、そういうわけにもいかないだろ……！　",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "177.2",
      "line_index": 177,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "4e5e57bf",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "こんなところで出したら……ぐっ！）",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "180.0",
      "line_index": 180,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "53b5fcbb",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "メアの舌が裏筋を舌先で小刻みに舐め、射精感がどんどん強くなっていく。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "181.0",
      "line_index": 181,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "a91f1e01",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "それでもみんながいる前で射精するわけにはいかない、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "181.2",
      "line_index": 181,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "a91f1e01",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "その一心で懸命に射精を堪え続ける。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "184.0",
      "line_index": 184,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "c7eb6e45",
      "speaker": "メア",
      "ja": "（我慢強い人……♥　そういう頑固なところも大好き……♥　",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "184.2",
      "line_index": 184,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "c7eb6e45",
      "speaker": "メア",
      "ja": "でもぉ……我慢は身体に毒です♥　",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "184.4",
      "line_index": 184,
      "inline_index": 4,
      "line_hash": "c7eb6e45",
      "speaker": "メア",
      "ja": "さあ遠慮なさらずにザーメンぴゅっぴゅしてください）",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "187.0",
      "line_index": 187,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "6c9f682e",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "（あ、あ……う、くうううっ！　メア、やめてくれ……！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "187.2",
      "line_index": 187,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "6c9f682e",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "もう……う、ううう……ふ、ふ、ふっ！！）",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
